320
00:17:16,420 --> 00:17:17,420
Come on, come on.

321
00:17:17,420 --> 00:17:18,420
Cheers.

322
00:17:18,420 --> 00:17:19,500
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

323
00:17:19,500 --> 00:17:21,060
- We'll drink first.
- Cheers.

324
