527
00:25:35,180 --> 00:25:36,380
Think about it.

528
00:25:36,380 --> 00:25:37,480
We're related by marriage.

529
00:25:37,660 --> 00:25:38,540
If we harm you,

530
00:25:38,540 --> 00:25:40,140
