00:31:16,500 --> 00:31:17,380
Lady Shen.

668
00:31:18,540 --> 00:31:19,420
Vice Prefect Lin.

669
00:31:20,060 --> 00:31:21,540
Ancestors,

670
00:31:22,060 --> 00:31:23,340
