795
00:37:19,380 --> 00:37:20,580
We're not at a dead end yet.

796
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:22,180
Let me carry you.

797
00:37:23,700 --> 00:37:24,540
Che,

798
00:37:24,940 --> 00:37:26,860
